{"id": 3071, "genre": 1000, "title": "你在生活中都见过哪些对“情绪”的误会？", "description": "哪些关于情绪的习惯性说法，你觉得其实不太对？（题图来自：iStock ©️ priyanka gupta）", "record_count": 6381, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191127010401MaDGEuk9L6lefBsP.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-11-26T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6068, "title": "你在生活中都见过哪些对“情绪”的误会？", "content": "你都见过哪些关于“情绪”的误会？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 349798, "content": "“表达自己的愤怒”就等于“发脾气”或者“喜欢吵架”", "image": "img/option/option/20191127003853DIsQ2tGMwfj8JKyV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349799, "content": "愤怒/伤心之类的情绪一定属于“负面感情/负能量”", "image": "img/option/option/20191127010546Z5M7wvhSjlIKTsP4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349800, "content": "把表达愤怒或不满理解成“闹情绪/生气也没有用”", "image": "img/option/option/20191127003949VAOzoy0xiQ7SvEB3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349801, "content": "成年人“应该时刻保持冷静”，表达情绪是件幼稚的事", "image": "img/option/option/20191127004949rTgJaq6HY8oGx421.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349802, "content": "朋友/伴侣间不能有任何争吵，否则就是“破坏感情”", "image": "img/option/option/20191127004919svjUNwFqlYoc3f5u.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349803, "content": "只有“不发脾气/性格好/能回避情绪”才能被叫做“情商高”", "image": "img/option/option/20191127004736IAmYcbahjBd1WZnV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349804, "content": "把“有情绪”强行等同于“不客观”，忽略情绪存在的合理性", "image": "img/option/option/20191127005212pe2K0VyhlUOfkXi4.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349805, "content": "“控制情绪”被过度简化成“像机器人一样没有情绪”", "image": "img/option/option/20191127004214GUAWae9HyTZ4XOLz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}